01:27:45,399 --> 01:27:47,050
{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs28\bord4}很好

880
01:27:47,081 --> 01:27:48,921
{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs28\bord4}抱歉

881
01:27:49,660 --> 01:27:52,113
