882
01:27:52,235 --> 01:27:53,604
{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs28\bord4}相当疼

883
01:27:53,993 --> 01:27:56,773
{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs28\bord4}另一方面  能流血

884
01:27:56,792 --> 01:27:59,686
